ğŸ“Œ 3. Dataset Description

This dataset includes booking information from two different hotels:

ğŸ¨ 1. City Hotel

Located in urban environment

Usually lower price (ADR)

High booking volume

More cancellations


ğŸ 2. Resort Hotel

Located in leisure/tourist area

Higher price (ADR)

Seasonal demand

Lower cancellation rates



