ğŸ“Œ 7. Summary for Phase 1

In Phase 1, we selected the Hotel Booking Demand dataset from Kaggle.This dataset contains 85,597 hotel booking records with 32 attributes.
It includes detailed information about booking dates, customer types, hotel types, pricing (ADR), and cancellations.
The dataset is suitable for analyzing booking patterns, customer behavior, price trends, and cancellation prediction.
It provides rich real-world data from two hotels â€” City Hotel and Resort Hotel â€” making it ideal for exploratory data analysis and predictive modeling.
